00:33:10.127 --> 00:33:11.667
because we have the Dead Sea Scrolls,

00:33:11.688 --> 00:33:13.808
but it's important to know that that is

00:33:13.909 --> 00:33:14.788
the case.

00:33:16.209 --> 00:33:21.270
So an important lesson is being taught

00:33:21.310 --> 00:33:21.530
